description:
Danny & special guest Troy Turner (Taste of Reality) talk #RHONY, Kim Zolciak's new song, & more. Danny also debuts the new Everything Iconic theme song by Kimberley "8th World Wonder" Locke called "Raise Your Hands."


Download the full version of "Raise Your Hands" at https://bit.ly/2uaiWRM
